 Scheduled several times per year.\n\n• Notes: The market often reacts 
 not only to the rate decision\, but also to the statement\, forecasts\, 
 press conference and tone.\n\n• Acronyms: FOMC = Federal Open Market C
 ommittee\; RBA = Reserve Bank of Australia.\n\nOfficial source: https://
 www.federalreserve.gov/newsevents/2026-june.htm
