 can quickly shift central-bank rate expectations.\n\n• Frequency: US C
 PI is monthly. Australian CPI has both monthly indicator releases and qu
 arterly CPI releases.\n\n• Notes: Core CPI removes volatile items such
  as food and energy to give a cleaner read on underlying inflation press
 ure.\n\n• Acronyms: CPI = Consumer Price Index.\n\nOfficial source: ht
 tps://www.abs.gov.au/statistics/economy/price-indexes-and-inflation/cons
 umer-price-index-australia
