 irectly affect interest rates\, currency valuation\, bond yields and equ
 ity risk appetite.\n\n• Frequency: Scheduled several times per year.\n
 \n• Notes: The market often reacts not only to the rate decision\, but
  also to the statement\, forecasts\, press conference and tone.\n\n• A
 cronyms: FOMC = Federal Open Market Committee\; RBA = Reserve Bank of Au
 stralia.\n\nOfficial source: https://www.federalreserve.gov/newsevents/2
 026-september.htm\n\nExplainer:\n• What it is: Central Bank Rate Decis
 ion\n\n• Measures: Interest-rate decision\, policy statement and guida
 nce from the central bank.\n\n• Usual market effect: More hawkish-than
